_:Ndb9c884631054ac5b3623f63ad03f8eb <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>BDUK became part of DSIT in November 2025. For guidance on how to raise a complaint, see <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-science-innovation-and-technology/about/complaints-procedure\">Complaints procedure - Department for Science, Innovation and Technology</a>.</p>\n\n<p>All other correspondence for the attention of BDUK should be sent to <a href=\"mailto:correspondence@dsit.gov.uk\">correspondence@dsit.gov.uk</a> and we will aim to provide a response within 20 working days.</p>\n\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
